			<ns0:name>pa...@google.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/101628056640429344673/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">The R-DFA validator allows %r15 as index, regardless of scale.
The production validator allows %r15 _only_ as base, even if scale==1. Same applies to %rsp and %rbp, whenever they are possible in instruction encoding.

The R-DFA must be changed to eliminate the difference.

